      <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none prose-headings:font-semibold prose-headings:tracking-tight prose-a:text-brand-600">

        <p>These Terms of Service (&ldquo;Terms&rdquo; or &ldquo;Agreement&rdquo;) constitute a legally binding agreement between you (&ldquo;you,&rdquo; &ldquo;your,&rdquo; or &ldquo;User&rdquo;) and BuildWorkPro LLC, a Florida limited liability company (&ldquo;BuildWorkPro,&rdquo; &ldquo;we,&rdquo; &ldquo;us,&rdquo; or &ldquo;our&rdquo;), governing your access to and use of the BuildWorkPro cloud-based construction management platform, including the web application, mobile applications, APIs, documentation, and all related services (collectively, the &ldquo;Platform&rdquo;).</p>

